<plot>Traveling salesman Martin Tripp gets fired from his job while in a small town. He decides to remain there and find work. He gets a job at the local general store and uses his city skills to make the store profitable. He has several adventures in the town, overcoming bank robbers and solving the mystery of a haunted church.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?013214</url></doc>
